{"article":"<section><h1 data-index=0>glob 路径匹配</h1><section><h2 data-index=1>glob 介绍</h2><p><a href=https://github.com/isaacs/node-glob>英文</a></p><p><a href=http://www.jianshu.com/p/ce7cf53274bb>中文</a></p></section><section><h2 data-index=2>监听所有目录，所有文件</h2><p>&#39;./src/**&#39;</p></section></section><section><h1 data-index=3>代码规范</h1><p><a href=https://eslint.org/ >https://eslint.org/</a></p><p><a href=https://github.com/standard/standard/blob/master/docs/README-zhcn.md>JavaScript Standard Style</a></p></section><section><h1 data-index=4>前端框架工具汇总</h1><section><h2 data-index=5>前端构建</h2><p>gulp 与 browserify<br>webpack<br>rollup</p></section><section><h2 data-index=6>各种js数据驱动框架</h2><ul><li>reactjs</li><li>vuejs</li><li><a href=https://github.com/developit/preact>Preact</a>：react 的轻量解决方案</li></ul></section></section><section><h1 data-index=7>浏览器跨域</h1><section><h2 data-index=8>h5 解决方案</h2><p>允许单个:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https:<span class=hljs-comment>//www.google.com</span>\n</code></pre><p>允许多个，逗号隔开:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https:<span class=hljs-comment>//www.google.com,https://www.baidu.com</span>\n</code></pre><p>允许所有:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\n</code></pre></section></section><section><h1 data-index=9>移动端web开发问题</h1><section><h2 data-index=10>ios 移动端 click 300ms 延迟解决</h2><p>文本框点击获焦也会出现延迟</p><p><strong>解决：</strong></p><p>head 中添加如下代码即可</p><pre><code class=lang-html><span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>meta</span> <span class=hljs-attr>name</span>=<span class=hljs-string>\"viewport\"</span> <span class=hljs-attr>content</span>=<span class=hljs-string>\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no\"</span>/&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><p>强调，必须带有<code>width=device-width</code><br>此方式也会禁止双击放大</p><p>当前测试系统为ios10，由于条件问题，其他低版本系统未测</p></section><section><h2 data-index=11>android webview 初始body 为0 问题</h2></section><section><h2 data-index=12>android webview 界面残留，界面闪烁</h2><p>关闭硬件加速</p></section></sectio